884
00:58:13,793 --> 00:58:14,864
Apa?

885
00:58:15,394 --> 00:58:18,403
Maksudku, betapapun gilanya kita, kita harus mengatakan hal yang benar.

886
00:58:18,403 --> 00:58:20,773
